null

What a year! 

1. Covid, baby! 

2. First MoCCA! 

3. Got engaged 💖

4. Went to Medieval Times afterwards and watched a horse poop (10/10 experience) 

5. First pride! 

6. Psych ward (again!)

7. Got a studio! 

8. Started tattooing! 

9. Went to San Francisco to cage dive with sharks! (Photo is the consequences of that decision). 

Glad that’s over with! Let’s all have a great 2023! Happy holidays, everybody!
